<font size="5">
<b>Fossil:</b>
<i>Simple, high-reliability, distributed software configuration management</i>
</font>
</p>

<h3>Why Use Fossil?</h3>

<table border="0" cellpadding="1" bgcolor="#558195" align="right" hspace="10">
<tr><td>
